The paper deals with an online problem of optimizing the movement of resources to serve demands, which involves algorithms, optimization, and decision-making. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Game Theory (cs.GT), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) sub-categories.
